document.discussion_title: Cloudy skies expected in Austin on Sunday
document.topic_text: Cloudy skies expected in Austin on Sunday American-Statesman Monday 25th April, 2016 After two days of sunshine and clear skies, a chance of rain returns to the Austin area Sunday.Those waking early will see fair skies, with only slight chances of rain at 20 percent, according to the National Weather Service. The best chance for thunderstorms will come after 1 p.m., meteorologists say. Clouds could dominate most of the day, and temperatures will reach a high near 79.Tonight, the rain chance will fall again to 20 percent, meteorologists say, with a low around 67....
